    dc:creator "Gültekin, Levent" ;
    dc:date "2008" ;
    dc:title "Taxonomic review of the stem-inhabiting trehala-constructing Larinus Dejean, 1821 (Coleoptera: Curculionidae): New species, systematics and ecology" ;
