<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.274126>
    dc:description "FIGURES 15 – 20. Life stages of L. capsulatus sp. n. (Aras Valley, 2003). 15 – oviposition mark; 16 – eggs in petiole; 17 – larva in capsule (trehala); 18 – capsules on stem; 19 – pupa in capsule (trehala); 20 – newly emerged adult." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/274126/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.274127>
    dc:description "FIGURES 21 – 26. Echinops orientalis, host plant of L. capsulatus sp. n. 22 – habitat of L. capsulatus sp. n. at Aras Valley. 23 – capsule (trehala) of L. rudicollis. 24 – new generation adult of L. rudicollis emerging from capsule. 25 – capsule of L. hedenborgi dorsal view; 26 – ventral view of capsule." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/274127/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

